items.name: Tuscan Kale Salad
items.description: A fresh Tuscan Kale Salad served with crisp Hudson Valley apples, toasted pumpkin seeds, crumbled goat cheese, and drizzled with balsamic vinaigrette.

items.name: Romaine Caesar Salad
items.description: A fresh Caesar salad made with crispy romaine lettuce, cherry tomatoes, roasted garlic, and a Parmesan crisp on top.

items.name: Cobb Wedge Salad
items.description: A hearty Cobb Wedge Salad with iceberg lettuce, smoked chicken, avocado, crispy bacon, blue cheese, a hard-boiled egg, and ranch dressing.

items.name: Mac N Cheese Lollipops
items.description: Crispy Mac N Cheese Lollipops made with a four-cheese blend and coated in panko breadcrumbs, served with a dipping sauce.

items.name: Warm Artichoke & Kale Dip
items.description: A creamy artichoke and kale dip served with crispy corn tortilla chips, perfect for dipping.

items.name: All Natural Beef Blend Burger
items.description: A juicy beef burger with crispy applewood smoked bacon, served on a soft bun with lettuce, tomato, and a side of fries.

items.name: Ahi Tuna Burger
items.description: A seared ahi tuna burger topped with sriracha tartar sauce, served on a toasted bun with fresh greens and a side of fries.

items.name: Chicken Sandwich
items.description: A grilled chicken sandwich topped with melted fontina cheese, crispy pancetta, fris√©e, and tomato aioli on a toasted bun, served with a side of fries.

items.name: Samosa
items.description: Crispy pastry stuffed with spiced potatoes and peas, served with chutney.

items.name: Pakoras
items.description: Crispy vegetable or paneer fritters coated in chickpea flour batter and deep-fried to perfection.

items.name: Pani Puri
items.description: Crispy hollow puris filled with tangy tamarind water, spices, and diced potatoes, served with extra tamarind water on the side.

items.name: Aloo Tikki
items.description: Spiced potato patties, crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, served with chutneys.

items.name: Chicken Tikka Masala
items.description: Grilled chicken chunks in a rich, spiced tomato-based sauce, garnished with fresh cilantro and served with naan.

items.name: Paneer Tikka Masala
items.description: Grilled paneer cubes in a rich, spiced tomato gravy, garnished with fresh cilantro, and served with naan or rice.

items.name: Saag Paneer
items.description: Creamy spinach curry with soft paneer cubes, garnished with fresh cream and cilantro, served with naan or rice.
